commit_message:
For changing partial key-value pair in resources

use this method to update some nested key-value pair in
some resources,for example,we can update the status in info dict of the
job_execution, or we can edit job start time for scheduled jobs.

job_config = {
    "info": {
        "status": "suspend"
    }
    "job_execution_info": {
        "start": "xxx"
    }
}

related bp: add-suspend-resume-ability-for-edp-jobs
related bp: blueprint api-for-objects-update
related bp: enable-scheduled-edp-jobs

